{"tid":636901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「補鑊$4,000」最快明年2月申請","createTime":"2018-04-21T10:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T12:39:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"99784ebdd3ccfff55042acc21603986c58a0015c","tid":636901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368258?_ga=2.103911168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368258%3F_ga%3D2.103911168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=r%2FK4vrnRJXPjt3c04LzrjQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=297aa72f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368258%3F_ga%3D2.103911168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=fad47935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368258?_ga=2.103911168.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月21日 <br />\n<br />\n「補鑊$4,000」最快明年2月申請<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/18679967.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2F18679967.jpg&h=854e21b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政司司長陳茂波<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】財政司司長陳茂波「補鑊拾遺」向合資格市民派發4,000元，最快明年2月1日接受申請，退稅或差餉寬減不足4,000元也獲發差額。政府又修訂估算，料最多300萬人受惠，涉款逾113億元，但需聘706名非公務員合約員工處理，行政費3.11億元。<br />\n<br />\n政府在提交立法會《2018年撥款條例草案》文件進一步釐清申請資格。申請人須年滿18歲及持香港身份證，毋須繳付2017至18年度薪俸稅，通常居港包括暫時離港出差、留學或求醫等，但移居海外人士、擁有非自住物業或在港持有多過一所物業，一律不合資格。若退稅額、自住物業差餉寬減或兩者合計都少於4,000元，則可獲補差額。<br />\n<br />\n綜援及高齡津貼受助人在預算案獲發額外兩個月津貼後，仍少於4,000元，同樣受惠差額補償。由於派錢以個人申請，如夫婦合計報稅，其中一方應毋須繳稅，若符合上述資格也可申請；需繳稅一方若退稅不足4,000元，如合資格也可申領差額，但申請人必須同意當局向有關部門核實資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/a0404a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2Fa0404a.gif&h=45f6cc14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n行政費逾3億<br />\n<br />\n政府料最多300萬人受惠，最快明年2月1日至4月30日接受申請，由在職家庭津貼辦事處執行。整個派錢計劃涉113.16億元，行政開支佔3.11億元，佔總派錢額2.83%，當中以1.6億元聘請706名非公務員合約員工，另涉41個由內部調配的職位。由於43萬名社會保障受助人經自動轉賬獲補差額，不涉額外費用，平均每宗派錢成本約121元。申請人須提供基本資料予在職津處核對，處方會就每宗申請發出結果通知書，款項會存入申請人銀行賬戶或親身領取支票。查詢可致電38971088。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n學者：私下收集「留底」屬違法<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n內地擬引入菲傭　港有加薪壓力"},{"pid":"22cb0f087e700e91a29ce7bcf7cd679370269c62","tid":636901,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d27cd6ff7036d7ae0748b1f75989eab3d78875","tid":636901,"uid":162783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"on9 明年 錢又細左"},{"pid":"bac1c1758b0911028e834b41d0a6578505a96512","tid":636901,"uid":15483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:21:53.000Z","msg":"2022 年收唔收到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c547672c662cbf44ad33a4338b521ebb067b9aa2","tid":636901,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"on9 明年 錢又細左"},{"pid":"e4506621a2578a4c4c3c5a764e5d59a3ca4f35bb","tid":636901,"uid":67468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"冇人想理理你呀，行埋一邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cea29950e2b66e55bf8c0891e7c7cf896e7dacf","tid":636901,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:26:00.000Z","m